<HEADLINE> Chinese President on China Reunification Policy </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SYDNEY, Australia, September 8 (Xinhua) -- Visiting Chinese
President Jiang Zemin Wednesday reaffirmed China's fundamental
policy of "peaceful reunification and one country, two systems" in
fulfilling the country's reunification.
</P>
<P>
"Facts have proved and will continue to prove that so long as
we firmly adhere to the principle of 'one country, two systems',
we will surely be able to accomplish the great cause of China's
complete reunification," Jiang said.
</P>
<P>
During a welcoming dinner hosted by the Chinese community in
Sydney, President Jiang said that the reunification of Taiwan with
China's mainland is a common aspiration and sacred mission of all
the Chinese people.
</P>
<P>
"Nothing can stop this trend," he said, adding "any attempt by
anyone or any force to separate Taiwan from China is doomed to
failure."
</P>
<P>
Jiang, who is here on the third leg of his state visit to
Australia, also briefed the overseas Chinese on the Sino-
Australian ties.
</P>
<P>
He described his talks with Australian Governor-General
William Deane and Prime Minister John Howard as "fruitful."
</P>
<P>
He expressed the belief that his visit will play a positive
role in promoting China-Australia relations.
</P>
<P>
He said the purpose of his visit is to further enhance the
friendship between the Chinese and Australian peoples, expand
bilateral cooperation and bring a China-Australia relationship of
long-term stability and sound development into the 21st century.
</P>
<P>
Jiang highly commended the role of the Chinese community in
Australia, saying they live in harmony with local people and have
made indelible contributions to building Australia.
</P>
<P>
They have also contributed to the friendship between the
Chinese and Australian peoples, he added.
</P>
<P>
President Jiang's wife Wang Yeping, Vice-Premier Qian Qichen
and his wife Zhou Hanqiong were among those present at the dinner.
</P>
<P>
Artists of the Chinese community presented their colorful
performance to President Jiang and his entourage. 
</P>
</TEXT>
