<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 8 (Xinhua) -- Chinese Vice-Premier Li
Lanqing met here today with Louis Gerstner Jr., chairman of the
IBM Corporation of the United States.
</P>
<P>
Li praised IBM's participation in the development of China's
information industry, and expressed the hope that the company
would strengthen cooperation with China.
</P>
