<HEADLINE> 11 Tamil Rebels Killed in Sri Lanka </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
COLOMBO, September 8 (Xinhua) -- Sri Lanka's Defense Ministry
said Wednesday government troops have killed 11 Tamil rebels of
