construction workers disturbed some key optic cable lines in
downtown Beijing, interrupting service between Beijing and seven
southern provinces and municipalities, as well as the operation of
some major banks.
</P>
<P>
Officials at today's meeting stressed that in order to
guarantee the success of the anniversary celebrations, governments
at various levels, departments, factories, schools should be
responsible for the protection of communication lines.
