<HEADLINE> Poland to Work for More Direct Foreign Investment in 1999 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WARSAW, September 7 (Xinhua) -- Direct foreign investment in
Poland reached 4.9 billion U.S. dollars in the first six months
this year, nearing that of the same period of last year, said Adam
Paw-Lowicz, director of the Polish National Foreign Investment
Bureau.
</P>
